OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FItall be a cold and blustery
OL,6,Fday, with a mixture of sunny spells
OL,7,Fand showers. Some of the showers will
OL,8,Fbe heavy, with hail and thunder and
OL,9,Falso falling as snow over the hills.
OL,10,FTemperatures widely below average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers gradually easing
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,14,Falong with the gusty wind. Prolonged
OL,15,Fclear spells will allow for a cold
OL,16,Fnight with frost and ice possible in
OL,17,Fplaces.
