OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA sunny but chilly start.
OL,6,FHowever, cloud will thicken from the
OL,7,Fwest through the morning with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain moving across much
OL,9,Fof Northern Ireland and Scotland
OL,10,Fduring the afternoon.
